HEADWORD: Nullifier
<hw>Nul"li*fi`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who nullifies
or makes void; one who maintains the right to nullify a contract by one
of the parties.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nullify</ent>⟦br⟧
